5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Chuwar"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Chuwar? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Chuwar, Karalee, Karana Downs and Mt Crosby. Our 5-star instructors help Chuwar students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Chuwar is a riverside acreage suburb that straddles the Brisbane and Ipswich city boundaries, positioned directly alongside the major Warrego Highway corridor. The suburb offers a unique contrast: deeply quiet, semi-rural residential streets that are perfect for foundational car control, abruptly giving way to one of Queensland's busiest high-speed freight arterials."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"Our instructors leverage this contrast to produce highly competent drivers. By building confidence on Chuwar's quiet acreage roads and the nearby College's Crossing precinct, learners safely transition onto the Warrego Highway and the Mt Crosby Road interchange. This dual exposure—rural calm and highway intensity—is perfect preparation for the Ipswich practical driving assessment."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Chuwar learners test at the Ipswich TMR Customer Service Centre. Free pickup from Chuwar, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5","children":"📍"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","stron